    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふっ……はっ…………ふっ……",
      "startTime": 27.6174802184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8508148234
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8508148234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、スマホを事務所に忘れちゃって。取りに来る\nついでに、自主練しようと思ったんですが……",
      "startTime": 39.51748149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.2508148234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "それより前から練習してた、っていうことかしら\nさくらちゃん、ご両親のために本当に頑張っているわね",
      "startTime": 48.1999986649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.16473823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "こんな姿を見せられたら\nますます好きになっちゃいますね",
      "startTime": 55.9980715633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.8314038794
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……い、今のは、客観的な意見というか……\nさくらは、本当にみんなから好かれてますし",
      "startTime": 63.3647372127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7314064225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうね。でも、あの振り付けの曲って\n当日の予定にはないけど……",
      "startTime": 74.4666668575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1341050824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、これって……。あの、遙子さん\nちょっと相談したいことがあるんですが……",
      "startTime": 83.3341050824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.3341050824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "startTime": 87.4007717491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4674429934
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4674429934
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.93410966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "お父さん、お母さん、今日は集まってくれてありがとう\n一年間のお礼を込めて、パーティーを企画しました！",
      "startTime": 95.93410966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.2674429934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさん達もいて\nちょっと緊張しちゃうかもだけど、一緒に楽しもうね",
      "startTime": 102.1007763267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1340964358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "お食事には、この一年間でさくらちゃんがお仕事で\n関わった、美味しいグルメをご用意いたしました～",
      "startTime": 109.8666622798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.8459105056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "わ～～～～！　美味しそう～～～～！\nこの中華まん、食べたかったんだ～",
      "startTime": 118.3125771722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.7792463821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ、さくらが一番はしゃいでるじゃない\nでは、最初に私達の自己紹介からですね",
      "startTime": 127.7792463821,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 10866.670890599991,
          "startTime": 138.6459172727
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7792463821
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3792428216
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.812576155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "なんでやねんっ！　もういいぜっ！\nどうも、ありがとうございましたー！",
      "startTime": 137.812576155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、スタッフさん達も\n拍手ありがとうございま～す！",
      "startTime": 144.212576155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0459135574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……結局、最後までツッコミが早かったけど……\nでは、次のコーナーです。さくら",
      "startTime": 156.6792468907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6792468907
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.6792468907
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "うん。次はお父さんとお母さんに\n私の小さい頃の話を聞いちゃうよ！",
      "startTime": 164.7459135574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終盤",
      "startTime": 168.912580224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.9792204422
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.9458860916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、そろそろ最後のコーナーです\nあっという間で、ちょっぴり名残惜しいんだけど……",
      "startTime": 175.9792194249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.8458860916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "改めて、お父さん、お母さん。一年間……ううん\nずっとずっと、私のために頑張ってくれて、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 188.9458860916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_51_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "もう、二人とも、泣くのは早いよ……。えへへ……",
      "startTime": 196.6458667639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kawasakiliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 204.1792000972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
